description.narrative: The foundation required to support a more robust and equitable system to deliver quality health services, remains a work-in-progress. The systematic and strategic removal of bottlenecks, increasing understanding of policy gaps and working in partnership with other concerned agencies, are the main contributing factors to progress witnessed over the calendar year. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/01/2020
